{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC11_FRE_650.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x199,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Fred! I went to ask for opinions about your bread!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, thank you! I'm sorry I made you do this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Please, tell me everything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Okay. Everyone really liked it. They said they've never eaten bread that good before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I thought this bread was amazing, too, when I first ate it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "It wasn't just delicious. I started tearing up while I was eating it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I see, good... I'm glad everyone liked it so much..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I put everything I had into making it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "It was a masterpiece that I might not ever be able to make again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "So I was right...<CR>Hmm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x144,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "H-Huh? Is something bothering you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "...Was that bread really something you wanted to make, Mr. Fred?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x148,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Uh, th-that's..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I can see that it took a lot of time and effort to make it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But can you make that bread every day?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x149,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Well, that's... Just making the dough took several days..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x14a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I used rare ingredients, too, so I couldn't possibly make it every day..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Then that also means it'll be really expensive..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "But I feel like that doesn't go along with the goal you told me about before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x173,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Y-You're absolutely right... To have people eat my bread every day..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x177,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "That was my only desire..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Rather than amazing bread that you can only make a few of, I think that making more regular bread..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Is much better. I'm sorry for saying that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x178,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "...No. I was so caught up in making the ultimate bread, I forgot about the most important thing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x179,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I failed as a baker...<CR>No, it's a bigger problem than that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I might've just been running away from my harsh reality, using the ultimate bread as an excuse..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* I'm such a bad human being."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I think I need to clear my head. Maybe I should take a vacation and go to some secluded mountain somewhere."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "All right! Now that that's decided, I need to prepare for the mountains!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, I didn't finish my story!<CR>Please listen till the very end!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I'm sorry. I have a tendency to lose track of things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Well, I don't know how to put this, but I really like your bread, Mr. Fred."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "I'd be so sad if I wasn't able to eat your bread."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "And there are other people who are waiting for your bread than just me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x144,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "People are waiting for my bread...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Yes! Marietta and Bell are also always looking forward to your bread!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x146,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Ms. Marietta..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "If you could make such incredible bread, just making normal bread would still be..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Would still be very amazing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "So please, bake us normal, delicious bread again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x176,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "...Thank you, Ms. Ayesha. I feel like I've finally come back to my starting point."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xb,
            "name_id": 0xb,
            "extra_id": 0x178,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "And what I can do from now on...<CR>I'll start thinking about that again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "(I wasn't able to express it well,<CR>so I wonder if he understood what<CR>I was trying to say...)"
        }
    ]
}